            "answer_text": "You don't have a tense on \u201dreturn\u201d and they have to match. He WILL STAY here until he returnS. He (always) STAYS here until he returnS. He IS STAYING here until he returnS. He STAYED here until he returnED. He WAS STAYING here until he returnED. He HAD STAYED here until he returnED. ",
